{"tid":929988,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推到完場】寄聖誕卡給在囚義士行動及信件收集細節 (截收日期：12月17日)","createTime":"2018-12-06T03:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T07:23:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b15b03508e34c0f2452c823103be801400b0a6","tid":929988,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"SOURCE：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/leungtinkei\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fleungtinkei&d=35v5%2BV5R0wjNmYl1b1mfCWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=bc26dbf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/leungtinkei</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/wjMts9vj/Edward-Leung.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FwjMts9vj%2FEdward-Leung.jpg&h=7742b524&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n步入12月，象徵即將又迎來另一年的聖誕。在一片歌舞昇平中，香港時局依然昏暗；普世歡騰，救主卻沒有降臨。<br />\n<br />\n救主未見，只有一位名叫梁天琦、靈魂赤誠的年輕人在三年前出現。梁天琦並非救世主，當時他仍只是一位生於壞時代的普通年輕人，分別在於 ── 他沒有坐困愁城，也沒有束手等待奇蹟，而是選擇站起來，開始拚搏。「既然沒有人能代表我們，那就由我們來代表自己」，只因一個簡單的念頭，他毅然親身參政，決心要將自己信奉的政治理念堂堂正正打進議會。往後日子裏，這位原本默默無聞的年輕人，把握每個機會讓人刮目相看。<br />\n<br />\n今日政治環境有如一溝絕望的死水，無力感瀰漫，使人灰心喪志。然而，在埋怨港人命途坎坷、不得眷顧之時，姑且毋忘我們至少擁有一眾肯犧牲、願意擔起香港命運的年輕人，包括梁天琦。漫長的重審已經展開，適逢強調感恩的節日，或許應當藉此時機執起筆，寫幾句話為天琦打打氣，告訴他一聲：我們依然銘記。<br />\n<br />\n【信箱地址】<br />\n郵政總局郵政信箱 8632 號 P.O. Box 8632, General Post Office<br />\n<br />\n【寫信須知】<br />\n聖誕卡寄送特別須知：<br />\n1. 卡片設計不可立體、附有任何電子零件、發聲零件、金粉、銀粉或彩粉<br />\n2. 卡上不可附有其他物件，如貼紙、郵票、剪報等，否則會被撕走<br />\n<br />\n普通信件寄送須知：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Eavyjm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Eavyjm&d=35v5%2BV5R0wjNmYl1b1mfCWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=9280a005\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Eavyjm</a>"},{"pid":"98a4d85eeb708f34f39398b0a59a446ba34dd753","tid":929988,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T03:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/D0ffkc4w/Edward-Leung-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FD0ffkc4w%2FEdward-Leung-2.jpg&h=4d5abf06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da4b90717af249453a2549791f2a2487c5077077","tid":929988,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38553e9e02d8ede931a354a663d6fc2c5211020c","tid":929988,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:25:59.000Z","msg":"反而想知天琦有咩想同我哋講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15fdd9a97d9e60861f6293bfa41a22822546d14","tid":929988,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c7d033a596612cb47d883a15547670f68c1cce","tid":929988,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:43:11.000Z","msg":"除咗天琦，仲會唔會畀其他義士？"},{"pid":"a0432049d5a7b33beb5260adca0022baad592135","tid":929988,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03c7d033a596612cb47d883a15547670f68c1cce","tid":929988,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:43:11.000Z","msg":"除咗天琦，仲會唔會畀其他義士？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:53:38.000Z","msg":"希望會有啦<br />\n<br />\n支那會都年年有聖誕卡寄去北京<br />\n(次次都被共匪掉晒)"},{"pid":"31182378dcaa61661b76cce2dfbaf5cdfc5efab7","tid":929988,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"仲有幾多人記得天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc8c3d583b4bbc49121b27872fa5b10def6dc6e","tid":929988,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:06:47.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"1a0a96f4f325d45544bfad23e939075b02308196","tid":929988,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:23:51.000Z","msg":","}]}